<br>
<i><font color="#FFFF00"><b>First</b></i></font> I wanna know who's out there. (good and evil)<br>
<br>
<i><font color="#FFFF00"><b>Second</b></i></font> Evil gets to be so boooooring without someone to <b><font size="4" color="#0000FF">harass</b></font>, <font size="2" color="#FF00FF">kidnap</font>, <font size="3" color="#00FF00"><i>mAiM</i></font>, <font size="1" color="#FF0000"><u>TORTURE</u></font>, or <font size="4" color="#00FFFF"><u>t</u><i>a</i><b>u</b><i>n</i><u>t</u></font>.  Have we all gotten so high a level that RP no longer matters to us like it did when we first started playing?<br>
<br>
What I want is an enemy.  Some goody goody upholding all that I loathe and seek to destroy, is that too much to ask?  Getting bored at spawn A? Send one of your enemies an IC tell insulting the filth that spawned them (make sure they know it's in RP, of course ;) )... it will be fun >=)<br>
<br>
<br>
<center><h3><font color="#00FF00">.,-'`*</font> <font color="#FF00FF"><i>So, here is what I propose</i></font><font color="#00FF00"> *`'-,.</font></h3></center><br>
 <br>
Perhaps have an event of RP guilds... get a GM or 2 involved to help pull it off.<br>
<br>
<i>Let's say...</i><br>
Evil has allied and captured/is capturing something sacred of the Good guilds - perhaps we are destroying someone's honor, taking a magical and powerful treasure, something... - and the Good guilds have to come and stop us from getting it/destroying it/etc depending on what IT is decided to be.  There will be a huge war of guilds.  If evil wins, then the skies turn red like blood and all the undead walk around as well as Avatars of our gods, something event-like and you know... evil, and if good wins, well... what would good want?  Rainbows and Erollisi Marr prancing around giving everyone flowered wreaths and <i>"I went to the Soandso Event and All I Got was This Lousy Breastplate"</i> T-Shirts?  I never see rainbows in EQ after it rains and I think that would be neat.<br>
<br>
After all is said and done, we can have an OOC mixer where we get drunk and just goof off.  Maybe have games and competitions.<br>
<br>
Well, I've rambled long enough and honestly dunno how to go about setting something of that magnitude up...<br>
<br>
Any thoughts?  Any interests? <p><center><img src="http://www.geocities.com/darkaurra/aurrasig2.JPG"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/umistressezra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mistress Ezra</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 698<br> <font color=#E9D756>(1/24/01 6:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrroleplayingoocforum.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=61.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /bonk HEY RP GUILDS</span><hr size=1> I am always interested and have tried... I hope this goes well.  HERE I AM <br>
