So here goes, We all know there's the new presence of the Gnomish pirates allowing transport to Velious, they are currently the only way to and from Velious.  Thus if the evils can wash them out and take over, they can control the flow of people to and from, however they choose to use that power (making Velious an evils playground, strandind all the goods there and leaving us with the Mainland, however we wanna do it).<br>
<br>
In order to accomplish this, the idea has been brought about to use the art of necromancy to raise that cluster of ships that are all sunken together in Timorous Deep.  The goods catch wind of this, evils would have to mount a defense of the Outpost for some time to buy the necros time to work their mojo.  From there I'm not certain where to take it, haven't really fleshed out the idea yet, it'd be a perfect event to bring the new Deadwater Pirates in on too as I for one would like to meet some of 'em <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Well, back to work.<br>
<br>
